data.name: Feebas

attacks.name: Surprise Attack
attacks.text: Flip a coin. If tails, this attack does nothing.

data.flavorText: It eats anything, so it can even live in polluted streams and lakes. No one pays any attention to it.

data.name: Feebas

attacks.name: Add-a-Dash
attacks.text: Flip 2 coins. For each heads, draw a card.

data.flavorText: It is a shabby and ugly Pokémon. However, it is very hardy and can survive on little water.

data.name: Feebas

abilities.name: Submerge
abilities.text: As long as this Pokémon is on your Bench, prevent all damage done to this Pokémon by attacks (both yours and your opponent's).

data.flavorText: Although unattractive and unpopular, this Pokémon's marvelous vitality has made it a subject of research.

data.name: Feebas

attacks.name: Splashing Dodge

data.flavorText: A tough Pokémon that is perfectly fine even in dirty water. However, due to its ragged, shabby appearance, it isn't popular.
